## CLI Skills

### Package Management
```bash
[package manager] install                # Install / sync all dependencies
[package manager] add [package]          # Requires explicit approval first
[package manager] remove [package]       # Requires explicit approval first
[package manager] ls [package]           # Verify installed version (read-only, always safe)
```

### Development
```bash
[dev server command]
[build command]
[preview command]
```

### Testing
```bash
[test-run-once command]        # Must pass before any task is complete
[test-single-file command]
[coverage command]
```

### Type Safety / Lint
```bash
[typecheck command]            # Must pass before any task is complete
[lint command]                 # Must pass with zero errors and zero warnings
```

