## Dependency Install Script Approval (pnpm-specific — remove if not using pnpm)

If `pnpm install` reports ignored/blocked build scripts, do not hand-edit
`pnpm-workspace.yaml`'s allowlist from memory. Run `pnpm approve-builds`,
review each flagged package, and commit the regenerated file. See the
comments inside `pnpm-workspace.yaml` for the full workflow — this is
security-relevant and version-dependent, so the interactive command is the
source of truth, not a remembered list.

