## When to Ask vs. When to Proceed

### Always ask before:
- Any dependency change (add/remove)
- Deleting any existing file
- Modifying build/type config (`tsconfig`, bundler config, CI workflow)
- Changing shared types or composables/hooks used across more than a few files
- Any change touching more than 3 existing files at once

### Proceed without asking:
- Any read-only command in this file
- Creating new files in existing feature directories
- Writing or updating test files
- Running the typecheck or lint command at any time

